      "description": "CopperKnob is an App which allows you to browse over 177,000 line dance stepsheets from the CopperKnob website.\n\nStepsheets can be saved locally for offline use when no internet connection is available. The app also includes the ability to create, manage, and browse lists of stepsheets, making it easier to organise favourites, downloads, or custom collections. In addition, stepsheets can be printed directly from the app.\n\nYou can search for stepsheets by title, choreographer, music, or any category.\n\nLists of the CopperKnob website’s most recent and most popular line dances are provided, along with music, demo, and tutorial videos for each stepsheet.\n\nNote: CopperKnob requires internet access to connect and view the live stepsheet archive.",
